testParse :: (String -> [LogMessage]) -> Int -> FilePath -> IO [LogMessage] #

testParse p n f tests the log file parser p by running it on the first n lines of file f.

testWhatWentWrong :: (String -> [LogMessage]) -> ([LogMessage] -> [String]) -> FilePath -> IO [String] #

testWhatWentWrong p w f tests the log file parser p and warning message extractor w by running them on the log file f.
